'''ESPN2'''是[[美國|美國]]的一個[[有線電視|有線電視]]和[[衛星電視|衛星電視]]頻道，由[[迪士尼公司|迪士尼公司]]成員[[ESPN公司|ESPN公司]]所有。ESPN2最初主要播出面向年輕的體育迷的節目。1990年代之後，頻道開始逐漸增加主流體育節目的比例。2015年2月。美國有94,379,000台電視可以收看ESPN2，佔收費電視總數的81.1%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/02/22/list-of-how-many-homes-each-cable-network-is-in-as-of-february-2015/366230/ |title=List of how many homes each cable network is in as of February 2015 |last=Seidman |first=Robert |work=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]] |publisher=Zap2it |date=February 22, 2015 |accessdate=February 23, 2015 |archive-date=2015-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151229025813/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/02/22/list-of-how-many-homes-each-cable-network-is-in-as-of-february-2015/366230/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。ESPN2開播於1993年10月1日<ref name="usatoday-keith">{{cite news |url=http://www.usatoday.com/sports/columnist/hiestand-tv/2007-08-23-Olbermann-NFL_N.htm |title=Olbermann's career veers onto NFL path |publisher=USA Today |accessdate=September 25, 2012 |first=Michael |last=Hiestand |date=August 28, 2007 |archive-date=2009-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108055240/http://www.usatoday.com/sports/columnist/hiestand-tv/2007-08-23-Olbermann-NFL_N.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 

